    <item>
      <title>威立雅利润因废物和水务服务需求增长而上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/veolia-profit-rises-on-growing-demand-for-waste-water-services</link>
      <description><![CDATA[威立雅环境集团上半年盈利因服务需求增长及成本削减而上涨 10%，使公司有望实现全年利润目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/veolia-profit-rises-on-growing-demand-for-waste-water-services</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 05:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>三星芯片主管警告称，除非做出改变，否则将陷入“恶性循环”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/samsung-chips-boss-warns-of-vicious-cycle-if-it-doesn-t-change</link>
      <description><![CDATA[三星电子公司芯片业务领导人在上任数月后向员工发出了一份异常严厉的备忘录，警告称，如果不改革企业文化，这家韩国最大的公司可能陷入“恶性循环”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/samsung-chips-boss-warns-of-vicious-cycle-if-it-doesn-t-change</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 05:21:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>人工智能蓬勃发展，默克半导体业务有望反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/merck-sees-rebound-for-semiconductor-business-amid-ai-boom</link>
      <description><![CDATA[默克公司表示，在人工智能浪潮的推动下，其半导体业务已到达转折点，并提供了有关该德国公司上调盈利预测的更多细节。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/merck-sees-rebound-for-semiconductor-business-amid-ai-boom</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 05:08:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>打击中国学生引发对英国科技雄心的担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/uk-university-crackdown-on-chinese-students-harms-country-s-tech-ambitions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一些商界领袖和学者担心，保护大学免受间谍活动侵害的运动会使该国的科学抱负面临风险。]]></description>
